data.description:
Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled within a quiet gated community.  As you step through the front door, you are greeted by a large open concept living area that is perfect for entertaining or relaxing with the family.  The kitchen has ample counter space for preparing large gourmet meals or simple afternoon snacks.  The breakfast nook allows for a nice size table, along with additional seating at the bar.  Inside you will find an abundance of closets and storage spaces ensuring a clutter-free and organized environment, catering to all your storage needs. The home boasts a cozy and warm ambiance, while outside you will find natural beauty around the community pond.  
Gate is closed 24-7 providing security and comfort for all residents.
